Class JSONMessageFactory

      • buildAlterTableMessage

        public AlterTableMessage buildAlterTableMessage(Table before,
                                                Table after)
        Description copied from class: MessageFactory
        Factory method for AlterTableMessage. Unlike most of these calls, this one can return null, which means no message should be sent. This is because there are many flavors of alter table (add column, add partition, etc.). Some are covered elsewhere (like add partition) and some are not yet supported.
        Specified by:
        buildAlterTableMessage in class MessageFactory
        Parameters:
        before - The table before the alter
        after - The table after the alter
        Returns:
